Document: RDPipelineColorBlendState
Path: godot/classes/class_rdpipelinecolorblendstate.rst
Summary: Represents a pipeline color blend state used by the RenderingDevice.

Inherits: RefCounted < Object
Pipeline color blend state (used by RenderingDevice). This class defines how color blending operations are performed during rendering, including source and destination blend factors, blend operations, and whether blending is enabled for specific color channels. It is part of the low-level rendering pipeline configuration system in Godot, allowing precise control over how colors are combined when rendering 3D objects.
---CHUNK---
