Path: godot/classes/class_rdpipelinecolorblendstate.rst  
Summary: Properties and member variables of the RDPipelineColorBlendState class, including their types, descriptions, and default values.  

attachments (Array<RDPipelineColorBlendStateAttachment>): Array of color blend state attachments. Default: [].  
blend_constant (Color): Color value used for blending operations. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1).  
enable_logic_op (bool): Enables or disables logic operations for blending. Default: false.  
logic_op (LogicOperation): Specifies the logic operation to apply. Default: 0 (equivalent to LogicOperation::CLEAR).
