Document: RDPipelineColorBlendState
Path: godot/classes/class_rdpipelinecolorblendstate.rst
Summary: Properties defining color blending behavior for a render pipeline, including attachments, blend constants, and logic operations.

attachments (Array<RDPipelineColorBlendStateAttachment>): The attachments that are blended together. Default: empty array. Set via set_attachments(value: Array<RDPipelineColorBlendStateAttachment>), retrieved via get_attachments().

blend_constant (Color): The constant color to blend with. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1). Set via set_blend_constant(value: Color), retrieved via get_blend_constant(). See also RenderingDevice.draw_list_set_blend_constants().

enable_logic_op (bool): If true, performs the logic operation defined in logic_op. Default: false. Set via set_enable_logic_op(value: bool), retrieved via get_enable_logic_op().

logic_op (LogicOperation): The logic operation to perform for blending. Only effective if enable_logic_op is true. Default: 0 (LogicOperation::CLEAR). Set via set_logic_op(value: LogicOperation), retrieved via get_logic_op(). LogicOperation enum values: 0 (CLEAR), 1 (SET), 2 (COPY), 3 (COPY_INVERTED), 4 (INVERT), 5 (AND), 6 (AND_INVERTED), 7 (AND_REVERSE), 8 (AND_INVERTED_REVERSE), 9 (OR), 10 (OR_INVERTED), 11 (OR_REVERSE), 12 (OR_INVERTED_REVERSE), 13 (NAND), 14 (NAND_INVERTED), 15 (NAND_REVERSE), 16 (NAND_INVERTED_REVERSE), 17 (NOR), 18 (NOR_INVERTED), 19 (NOR_REVERSE), 20 (NOR_INVERTED_REVERSE), 21 (XOR), 22 (XOR_INVERTED), 23 (XOR_REVERSE), 24 (XOR_INVERTED_REVERSE), 25 (EQUIV), 26 (EQUIV_INVERTED), 27 (EQUIV_REVERSE), 28 (EQUIV_INVERTED_REVERSE), 29 (AND_NAND), 30 (AND_NAND_INVERTED), 31 (AND_NAND_REVERSE), 32 (AND_NAND_INVERTED_REVERSE), 33 (OR_NOR), 34 (OR_NOR_INVERTED), 35 (OR_NOR_REVERSE), 36 (OR_NOR_INVERTED_REVERSE).